<%- include("partials/header.ejs") -%>
<link href="/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
    .bd-placeholder-img {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      text-anchor: middle;
      -webkit-user-select: none;
      -moz-user-select: none;
      user-select: none;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .bd-placeholder-img-lg {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>

  
</head>
<body class="bgs">
  
<main>
<div class="container py-4">
  <header class="pb-3 mb-4 border-bottom">
      <p class="fs-4 d-flex align-items-center text-light text-decoration-none"><%= name %> Plan for Today </p>
    
  </header>
  <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-light rounded-3">
    <div class="container-fluid py-5">
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Sign up</h1>
      <p class="col-md-8 fs-4">Sign up to MonsterWorkout and become a member of the MonsterClub. As a memeber you are able to save workouts, create custom plans, keep track of your progress, and more.</p>
      <button href="/register" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" type="button">Click here</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="h-100 p-5 text-white bg-dark rounded-3">
        <h2>Start a Random Workout</h2>
        <p>MonsterWokrout's random workout feature creates a customized workout depending on what body part you want to work on for the day. Try it out and see what exercise you get.</p>
        <a href="/random"><button  class="btn btn-outline-danger" type="button">Randomize</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-light border rounded-3">
        <h2>Create a Workout</h2>
        <p>Want to become a self-made monster and create your own worokut? Search through our catolog of exercises and pick the ones that will benefit you the most.</p>
        <a href="/search"><button class="btn btn-outline-danger" type="button">Create</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="pt-3 mt-4  text-danger border-top">
    J-Kizzy
  </footer>
</div>
</main>


  
</body>
</html>